WEBVTT

00:00:06.539 --> 00:00:09.450
Buvingiz sizni yoshligidagi jasurligi 
bilan lol qoldirsa ham,

00:00:09.450 --> 00:00:13.364
siz buvingiz trapez ustasi bo'lganiga
ishonishingiz qiyin bo'lsa kerak.

00:00:13.364 --> 00:00:18.344
Ammo bel va tirsakdagi og'rig', qariyalar
orasida keng tarqalgan tizza qirsillashi

00:00:18.344 --> 00:00:20.497
shunchaki “qarilik” emas.

00:00:20.497 --> 00:00:25.157
Aslida, bog'imdagi qotish holati 
ko'plab yoshlarni ham azoblantiradi.

00:00:25.157 --> 00:00:26.838
Sabachisi artrit.

00:00:26.838 --> 00:00:29.974
Bu kasallik bo’g’imlarda yallig’lanish va
og’riq keltiradi.

00:00:29.974 --> 00:00:33.694
AQShda 90 million kishilarda mavjud.